  ; ---- Net connections (summary) ----
  ; ESP32-C3 SPI1 (GPIO8/9/10/18) → ADS122U04 CS/SCLK/MISO/MOSI
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO19 ← ADS122U04 DRDY (interrupt)
  ; ESP32-C3 I2C (GPIO1/0) → SSD1306 OLED + BME280
  ; ESP32-C3 SPI2 (GPIO20/21/11/12) → microSD
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO4 → Q1 gate (column heater PWM, LEDC Timer 0)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO3 → Q2 gate (preconcentrator heater PWM, LEDC Timer 1)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO2 → Q3 gate (pump PWM, LEDC Timer 2)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO15 → Q4 gate (3-way valve)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO16 → Fan (GPIO output, cooldown blower)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO5  ← TH1 (ADC1_CH4, column temp)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO6  ← TH2 (ADC1_CH6, preconc temp)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO7  ← TH3 (ADC1_CH7, TCD body temp)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO13 ← Battery divider (ADC1_CH3)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO14 → WS2812B RGB LED (RMT)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO0  ← RUN button (BOOT, pull-up, falling-edge IRQ)
  ; ESP32-C3 GPIO17 ← MODE button (pull-up, falling-edge IRQ) / TP4056 CHRG

  ; ---- Power nets ----
  ; VBAT (3.7V) → MCP1640B → V5P0 (5V boost rail for pump + heaters)
  ; VBAT → AP2112 → V3P3 (3.3V digital rail: ESP32-C3, OLED, SD, ADS digital)
  ; VBAT → LP5907 → V1P8 (1.8V analog rail: ADS analog, TCD bridge ref)
  ; USB-C 5V → TP4056 → VBAT (charging)

  ; ---- Decoupling ----
  ; 100nF on every IC VDD pin (15 total)
  ; 10µF tantalum on each regulator output (5 total)
  ; 1µF on ADS122U04 AVDD + DVDD
  ; 10µH inductor on MCP1640B boost

)